ated><title>在哪里预订新款 Surface Laptop Studio 2 和 Laptop Go 3</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;微软 Surface Laptop Studio 2 的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/p5HEiLDESLjH-7P24BvlQRGDd9U=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72673177/DSCF3352.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;微软的 Surface Laptop Studio 2 看起来是之前型号的小幅更新，具有更快的性能和新的连接选项。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;hXpQAU&quot;>;微软宣布 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/21/23878658/microsoft -surface-laptop-studio-2-price-release-date&quot;>;Surface Laptop Studio 2&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/21/23881978/microsoft- Surface-laptop-go-3-price-release-date&quot;>;Surface Laptop Go 3&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/21/23882273/microsoft- event-surface-windows-office-ai&quot;>;最近在纽约举行的硬件活动&lt;/a>;，介绍了这两款笔记本电脑以及一系列&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/ 21/23883798/microsoft-copilot-unified-windows-11-apps-launch-date&quot;>;适用于 Windows 11、Microsoft 365 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge. com/2023/9/21/23873690/microsoft-new-ai-features-bing-search-shopping-dall-e-3&quot;>;必应&lt;/a>;。高端Surface Laptop Studio 2起价为1,099美元，而Surface Laptop Go 3起价为799美元；两者均定于美国东部时间 10 月 3 日上午 12 点发布。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;hu9Wj4&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot; readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Microsoft Surface 事件：6 大公告&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/ 9/21/23882074/microsoft-surface-copilot-event-2023-biggest-announcements&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Surface Go 4 带来了急需的性能提升&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/2023/9/21/23880536/microsoft-surface-go-4-convertible-price-release-date&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;Kc36O1&quot;>;虽然即将推出的笔记